channel.title: Free to use 562 client w/ all stuff working & id list
channel.description:
Ok guys I know this may seem pointless to release but it helps get some players on my server sometimes and helps people get a client that works very nicely for their server thats [u]Open Source[/u] :)
Anyway, You can use this for anything because its open source.
To change the ip for the server you need to go to \src\client.java When you get in that file press ctrl+f and search for [code]Class131_Sub2_Sub7.aString5636 = "rs.electricscape.com";[/code] Change rs.electricscape.com to the ip address of your server. Once done your free to use it
Virus scan: [IMG]http://i35.tinypic.com/a2dx5f.png[/img]
Its too large to post on virustotal
[url=http://electricscape.com/updater/ServerClient.EXE][u][size=36pt]Download[/size][/u][/url]
